    <releaseNotes># Version 4.0.0

================

## New Features

* Support connecting to Webex cloud registered systems.

## Changes

* Improve ultrasonic pairing performance and resilience.
* Minor updates to UI.

## Bugfixes

* Fix crashes occuring on certain systems, as reported by user marcis.U.
* Prevent reconnection issues in certain scenarios where there are multiple devices in the same room.

================

# Version 3.1.0

================

## Changes

* Added host fingerprint verification. See this help page on fingerprint matching for more information.
* Updates to external dependencies.
* Remove hardcoded lookup path from Qt5Core.dll to fix CVE-2021-1240.

## Bugfixes

* Fixed possible crash on application exit.

================

# Version 3.0.8

================

## Bugfixes

* Handle screen changes (screen added/remove/resized) better.
* Make correct error message appears in certain error scenarios.
* Try to ensure that app is always re-launched correctly on MacOS.

================

# Version 3.0.7

================

## Changes

* Take steps to reduce likelyhood of incorrectly decoding pairing messages in random noise
* Add option to disallow connections to public IP addresses
* Show volume button as muted when volume is set to zero
* For more details, see [the release notes](https://community.cisco.com/t5/mobile-applications-documents/proximity-3-0-7-release-notes/ta-p/4030791) on our support forums.

================

# Version 3.0.6

================

## Changes

* Compatible with new MacOS Catalina requirements.
* Minor changes to logging detail levels.

## Bugfixes

* Fix sharing indicator sizing issue in some mixed screen DPI scenarios.

================

# Version 3.0.5

================

## Changes

* Reduce amount of logging, especially metrics.

## Bugfixes

* Remove several potential crash scenarios.
* Minor bugfixes.

================

# Version 3.0.4

================

## Bugfixes

* Fix cursor scaling and positioning on MacOS.
* Minor bugfixes.
